description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 53, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 159, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, 8 for East, Box for South, and 5 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10533-38450-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [159 Votes, Top 10% Score]
